title UC-13: Elderly Living Alone (Activity)

|Case Worker|
start
:Login to SCP;
if (Authenticated?) then (no)
  stop
endif

:Select "Social Protection" Vertical;
if (Scope: Geo-Region OK?) then (no)
  :Access Denied (Scope Violation);
  stop
endif

